- **9:30 PM** - Reception concludes

## RSVP Information

Please let us know if you can join us by **July 15th, 2025**

**RSVP Options:**
- Fill out our contact form: [Insert contact form link]
- Call or text William: (803) 414-9580
- Call or text India: (803) 445-3200

**Please include:**
- Number of guests attending
