## Additional Information

**Accommodations:** We recommend finding accommodations near either the ceremony location (Boston Public Garden area) or the reception venue (Stoneham area) for your convenience.

**Registry:** Your presence is our present! We're just excited to celebrate with you.

**Questions?** Feel free to reach out to us:
- William: (803) 414-9580
- India: (803) 445-3200

We cannot wait to celebrate with you and create beautiful memories together!

With love and excitement,

**India & William**

---

*P.S. We're so grateful to have you in our lives and hope you can be part of our special day!*`;
---

<Layout title="India and Will Wedding &#9825;">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <div class="couple-names">India & William</div>
                <div class="wedding-text">are getting married!</div>
                <div class="date-highlight">August 23rd, 2025</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Wedding Details</h2>
            <div class="details-grid">
                <div class="detail-card">
                    <div class="detail-title">üå∏ Ceremony</div>
                    <div class="detail-text">
                        <strong>Saturday, August 23rd, 2025</strong><br>
                        4:00 PM - 5:00 PM<br>
                        Japanese Lantern<br>
                        Boston Public Garden
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-card">
                    <div class="detail-title">üéâ Reception</div>
                    <div class="detail-text">
                        <strong>Same Day</strong><br>
                        6:00 PM - 9:30 PM<br>
                        225a Fallon Road<br>
                        Stoneham, MA
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-card">
                    <div class="detail-title">üëó Dress Code</div>
                    <div class="detail-text">
                        Smart casual to cocktail attire<br>
                        (No black tie required)<br><br>
                        <em>We'll be outdoors for the ceremony, so please dress comfortably for the weather!</em>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Schedule of Events</h2>
            <div class="timeline">
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-time">3:30 PM</div>
                    <div class="timeline-event">Guest arrival at Japanese Lantern</div>
                    <div class="timeline-details">
                        <h4>Ceremony Details:</h4>
                        <p>Since we're celebrating in a public park, seating is limited. We'll provide picnic blankets and some chairs, but we encourage guests to bring their own seating if preferred.</p>
                        <p>Thank you for understanding the venue's natural limitations!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-time">4:00 PM</div>
                    <div class="timeline-event">Wedding ceremony begins</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-time">5:00 PM</div>
                    <div class="timeline-event">Ceremony concludes, travel time to reception</div>
                    <div class="timeline-details">
                        <h4>Reception & Transportation:</h4>
                        <p>Dinner, beverages, and dessert will be served at our reception venue, about 20-30 minutes from the ceremony. We recommend using Uber, taxi, or car service between locations, as parking is limited.</p>
                        <p>If you prefer to drive, there are public garages across the street at Boston Common, and the venue is also accessible via MBTA public transit.</p>
                        <div class="highlight">
                            <strong>Need help with transportation?</strong> Please reach out to us ahead of time‚Äîwe're happy to coordinate!
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-time">6:00 PM</div>
                    <div class="timeline-event">Reception begins at 225a Fallon Road, Stoneham</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-time">9:30 PM</div>
                    <div class="timeline-event">Reception concludes</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section rsvp-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">RSVP Information</h2>
            <p class="rsvp-instructions">
                Please include the name and number of guests attending and any dietary restrictions or special accommodations needed.
            </p>
            <div class="rsvp-deadline">Please respond by July 15th, 2025</div>
            
            <form name="wedding-rsvp" method="POST" netlify netlify-honeypot="bot-field" class="contact-form">
                <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="wedding-rsvp" />
                
                <!-- Honeypot field -->
                <p class="hidden">
                    <label>Don't fill this out if you're human: <input name="bot-field" /></label>
                </p>

                <h3 class="form-title">RSVP for India & William</h3>
                
                <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="name" class="form-label">Your Name <span class="required">*</span></label>
                        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" class="form-input" required />
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="email" class="form-label">Email Address <span class="required">*</span></label>
                        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="form-input" required />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="guests" class="form-label">Number of Guests <span class="required">*</span></label>
                        <select id="guests" name="guests" class="form-select" required>
                            <option value="">Select number of guests</option>
                            <option value="1">1 Guest</option>
                            <option value="2">2 Guests</option>
                            <option value="3">3 Guests</option>
                            <option value="4">4 Guests</option>
                            <option value="5+">5+ Guests</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="phone" class="form-label">Phone Number</label>
                        <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" class="form-input" />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="form-label">Which events will you attend? <span class="required">*</span></label>
                    <div class="checkbox-group">
                        <label class="checkbox-item">
                            <input type="checkbox" name="attending" value="ceremony" required />
                            <span class="checkbox-label">Wedding Ceremony (4:00 PM - Japanese Lantern, Boston Public Garden)</span>
                        </label>
                        <label class="checkbox-item">
                            <input type="checkbox" name="attending" value="reception" />
                            <span class="checkbox-label">Reception (6:00 PM - 225a Fallon Road, Stoneham, MA)</span>
                        </label>
                        <label class="checkbox-item">
                            <input type="checkbox" name="attending" value="both" />
                            <span class="checkbox-label">Both Ceremony & Reception</span>
                        </label>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="dietary" class="form-label">Dietary Restrictions or Allergies</label>
                    <textarea id="dietary" name="dietary" class="form-textarea" 
                        placeholder="Please let us know about any dietary restrictions, food allergies, or special meal requirements..."></textarea>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="message" class="form-label">Additional Message</label>
                    <textarea id="message" name="message" class="form-textarea" 
                        placeholder="Any special requests, questions, or just a sweet message for the happy couple..."></textarea>
                </div>
                
                <button type="submit" class="form-submit">Send RSVP</button>
            </form>
        
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Additional Information</h2>
            <div class="details-grid">
                <div class="detail-card">
                    <div class="detail-title">üè® Accommodations</div>
                    <div class="detail-text">
                        We recommend finding accommodations near either the ceremony location (Boston Public Garden area) or the reception venue (Stoneham area) for your convenience.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-card">
                    <div class="detail-title">üöó Getting Around</div>
                    <div class="detail-text">
                        <strong>Between Ceremony & Reception:</strong><br>
                        The reception is about 20-30 minutes from the ceremony. We recommend rideshare or taxi service for the easiest travel.
                        <br><br>
                        <strong>Parking Options:</strong><br>
                        ‚Ä¢ Public garages across from Boston Common<br>
                        ‚Ä¢ MBTA public transit available<br>
                        ‚Ä¢ Limited street parking
                        <br><br>
                        <strong>Need a ride?</strong> Reach out to us ahead of time and we'll help coordinate carpools!
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-card">
                    <div class="detail-title">üéÅ Registry</div>
                    <div class="detail-text">
                        Your presence is our present! We're just excited to celebrate with you.
                        As we start this new chapter together, we're saving for our honeymoon and a down payment on our first home. If you'd like to contribute to these dreams, we'd be deeply grateful‚Äîjust reach out to either of us directly. Of course, thoughtful gifts are always welcome and appreciated too.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Engagement Gallery</h2>
            <Gallery />
        </section>
        <footer class="footer">
            <p class="footer-main">
                We cannot wait to celebrate with you and create beautiful memories together!
            </p>
            <p class="footer-love">
                With love and excitement <span class="heart">‚ô•</span>
            </p>
            <p class="footer-names">
                India & William
            </p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</Layout>

    <script>
        // Add interactivity for checkboxes
        document.querySelectorAll('.checkbox-item input[type="checkbox"]').forEach(checkbox => {
            checkbox.addEventListener('change', function() {
                const item = this.closest('.checkbox-item');
                if (this.checked) {
                    item.classList.add('checked');
                } else {
                    item.classList.remove('checked');
                }
            });
        });

        // Handle "both" option logic
        document.querySelector('input[value="both"]').addEventListener('change', function() {
            const ceremonyBox = document.querySelector('input[value="ceremony"]');
            const receptionBox = document.querySelector('input[value="reception"]');
            
            if (this.checked) {
                ceremonyBox.checked = false;
                receptionBox.checked = false;
                ceremonyBox.closest('.checkbox-item').classList.remove('checked');
                receptionBox.closest('.checkbox-item').classList.remove('checked');
            }
        });

        // Uncheck "both" if individual events are selected
        document.querySelectorAll('input[value="ceremony"], input[value="reception"]').forEach(checkbox => {
            checkbox.addEventListener('change', function() {
                if (this.checked) {
                    const bothBox = document.querySelector('input[value="both"]');
                    bothBox.checked = false;
                    bothBox.closest('.checkbox-item').classList.remove('checked');
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
